(5943, '12', '86', NULL, '12. And the earth which splits (with the\ngrowth of trees and plants). ', 'en', '2019-11-04 09:40:08', '2019-11-04 09:40:08'),
(5944, '13', '86', NULL, '13. Verily, this (the Qur’ân) is the Word \nthat separates (the truth from falsehood, and  \ncommands strict laws for mankind to cut the\nroots of evil).', 'en', '2019-11-04 09:40:08', '2019-11-04 09:40:08'),
