(5949, '1', '87', NULL, '1. Glorify the Name of your Lord, the \nMost High, ', 'en', '2019-11-04 09:40:08', '2019-11-04 09:40:08'),
(5950, '2', '87', NULL, '2. Who has created (everything), and then \nproportioned it. .', 'en', '2019-11-04 09:40:08', '2019-11-04 09:40:08'),
(5951, '3', '87', NULL, '3. And Who has measured (preordainments \nfor everything even to be blessed or wretched);\nand then guided (i.e. showed mankind the\nright as well as the wrong paths, and guided\nthe animals to pasture).', 'en', '2019-11-04 09:40:08', '2019-11-04 09:40:08'),
(5952, '4', '87', NULL, '4. And Who brings out the pasturage,', 'en', '2019-11-04 09:40:08', '2019-11-04 09:40:08'),
(5953, '5', '87', NULL, '5. And then makes it dark stubble. ', 'en', '2019-11-04 09:40:08', '2019-11-04 09:40:08'),
(5954, '6', '87', NULL, '6. We shall make you to recite (the \nQur’an), so you (O Muhammadصلى الله عليه \nوسلم) shall not forget (it),', 'en', '2019-11-04 09:40:08', '2019-11-04 09:40:08'),
(5955, '7', '87', NULL, '7. Except what Allah may will. He knows \nwhat is apparent and what is hidden.', 'en', '2019-11-04 09:40:08', '2019-11-04 09:40:08'),
(5956, '8', '87', NULL, '8. And We shall make easy for you (O \nMuhammad صلى الله عليه وسلم) the easy way \n(i.e. the doing of righteous deeds).', 'en', '2019-11-04 09:40:08', '2019-11-04 09:40:08'),
(5957, '9', '87', NULL, '9. Therefore remind (men) in case the\nreminder profits (them).', 'en', '2019-11-04 09:40:08', '2019-11-04 09:40:08'),
(5958, '10', '87', NULL, '10. The reminder will be received by him \nwho fears (Allâh),', 'en', '2019-11-04 09:40:08', '2019-11-04 09:40:08'),
(5959, '11', '87', NULL, ' 11. But it will be avoided by the wretched, ', 'en', '2019-11-04 09:40:08', '2019-11-04 09:40:08'),
(5960, '12', '87', NULL, '12. Who will enter the great Fire (and will \nbe made to taste its burning). ', 'en', '2019-11-04 09:40:08', '2019-11-04 09:40:08'),
