(6189, '1', '105', '[1] (V.104:1) See the footnotes A, B, C, of (V.49:12).', '1. Have you (O Muhammad صلى الله عليه \nوسلم) not seen how your Lord dealt with the\nowners of the Elephant? [The Elephant army\nwhich came from Yemen under the command\nof Abrahah Al-Ashram intending to destroy\nthe Ka ‘bah in Makkah].', 'en', '2019-11-04 09:40:10', '2019-11-04 09:40:10'),
