(6205, '1', '108', '[4] (V.108:1) Narrated Anas رضى الله عنه » When the Prophet صلى الله عليه وسلم was made to ascend\nto the heavens. Heصلى الله عليه وسلم  said (after his return), “| came upon a river (in Paradise) the\nbanks of which were made of tents of hollow pearls. | asked Jibri! (Gabriel), ‘What is this\n(river)?’ He replied, ‘This is Al-Kauthar.''” (Sahih Al-Bukhari, Vol.6, Hadith No. 488).', '1. Verily, We have granted you (O \nMuhammad صلى الله عليه وسلم) Al-Kauthar (a\nriver in Paradise),[4]', 'en', '2019-11-04 09:40:10', '2019-11-04 09:40:10'),
