(6207, '3', '108', '[1] (V. 408:3) Narrated Anas رضى الله عنه The Prophet صلى الله عليه وسلم said, “None of you will\nhave Faith till he loves me more than his father, his children and all mankind. (Sahih\nAl-Bukhari, Vol.1, Hadith No.14).', '3. For he who hates you (O Muhammad \nصلى الله عليه وسلم) he will be cut off (from\nposterity and every good thing in this world\nand in the Hereafter).[1]', 'en', '2019-11-04 09:40:10', '2019-11-04 09:40:10'),
(6208, '1', '109', NULL, '1. Say: (O Muhammad صلى الله عليه وسلم to\nthese Mushrikûn and Kafirûn): “O Al-Kafirtûn\n(disbelievers in Allâh, in His Oneness, in His\nAngels, in His Books, in His Messengers, in\nthe Day of Resurrection, and in Al-Qadar.)!', 'en', '2019-11-04 09:40:10', '2019-11-04 09:40:10'),
